    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reviews</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >”…even in its current state, it’s already one of the more captivating multiplayer shooters on Steam right now.” <strong>IGN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“BattleBit has echoes of what Eric Barone did with Stardew Valley: a small game that punches above its weight and wins people over with unexpected depth and quality.” <strong>PC Gamer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“If you’ve grown tired of extraction shooters and battle royale games and crave something more focused on gunplay, combat, and just having fun over grinding and seasons, I’d recommend <i>BattleBit Remastered</i>.” <strong>Kotaku</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏简介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《*BattleBit Remastered*》，参与多达 254 玩家的混乱大型 FPS 战斗！无论你是用突击兵冲锋陷阵，还是作为支援兵构建关键防御，每个角色在这个低边形、紧张刺激的战场上都扮演着重要的角色。使用开放语音聊天与队友协作，并利用完全可破坏的环境来摧毁城市。你准备好迎接终极团队战争的挑战了吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可破坏的场景</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/8cff82274c102c808f6befc81329c82d.poster.avif?t=1730393449\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/8cff82274c102c808f6befc81329c82d.webm?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/8cff82274c102c808f6befc81329c82d.mp4?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>拆毁墙壁、建筑坍塌，利用动态的「环境变化」机制来改造战场，你的每个行动都会对周遭地域产生持久影响</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完全自订武器（进行中）</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/ae6dfbe685917e39f5d2d4468f494a74.poster.avif?t=1730393449\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/ae6dfbe685917e39f5d2d4468f494a74.webm?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/ae6dfbe685917e39f5d2d4468f494a74.mp4?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在《*BattleBit Remastered*》中，依照你的风格打造自己的专属武器！从瞄具、握把到枪管、弹匣，随心调整。打造最理想的武器配置，轻松主宰每场战斗局势。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>254 人大型伺服器</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/611117d20181595cbd811c9fa4f71487.poster.avif?t=1730393449\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/611117d20181595cbd811c9fa4f71487.webm?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/611117d20181595cbd811c9fa4f71487.mp4?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>参与最多 254 名玩家盛大规模的战斗！ 《*BattleBit Remastered*》提供庞大的多人伺服器，并透过近距离语音聊天让每场交锋都充满临场感！制定战术或挑衅敌人，在瞬息万变的战场上争夺霸权！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>坦克、直升机、运输与海上运输工具的激烈战斗</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/2a3d88b00e1fda35b473ad6016327d4d.poster.avif?t=1730393449\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/2a3d88b00e1fda35b473ad6016327d4d.webm?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/2a3d88b00e1fda35b473ad6016327d4d.mp4?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>掌控多种运输工具，主宰战场！从坦克、直升机到运输与海上运输工具，《*BattleBit Remastered*》带来激烈的载具战斗，为每场战争增添全新的战略深度与混乱感。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
